radiographic_examinations.findings: Ms. W was able to start eating soft foods 2 weeks after surgery; she experienced some nausea after eating, which resolved over a few months. Specific foods caused mild dumping symptoms.
radiographic_examinations.changes_over_time: By 12 months after surgery, she had lost 83 lb. At 18-month follow-up, she had lost an additional 17 lb. Two years after surgery, she had regained 6 lb.
